cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with action recognition in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The addition of a human pose estimation branch also suggests a focus on body movement and posture, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multi-task training and fusion of predictions could also relate to multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
